  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK276">
<l>neñciṟ ṟuṟavār tuṟantārpōl vañcittu</l>
<l>vāḻvāriṉ vaṉkaṇā ril</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Amongst living men there are none so hard-hearted as those who without to saking (desire) in their heart, falsely take the appearance of those who have forsaken (it).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
